name: iori's eyes - Double Soul Reloaded
description:
Iori's Eyes
Double Soul Reloaded

It's a card with a personalized code to download the album.

Released on october 24th 2012, six month after the beginning of the tour to present our debut album, Double Soul,   our new project is Double Soul Reloaded, a collection  of remixes by DJs and producers performing on the Italian scene.

Musicians as Antiteq, Aucan, Digi G'alessio, Esperanza, Glenda Mallory, Italoconnection, Origami, Parker Madicine, Pink Holidays, Poana Mozzi, Populous, SPCNVDR x 4SICSX, Thelicious, Uabos have been joining this project. They have been remixing Double Soul's tracks implying different attitudes and opposite styles, all of them interpreting our songs in a very personal way.

If you have any problems while downloading, please contact us at:
ioriseyes@yahoo.it

Thanks!
